{"tid":1011534,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"[歌唱] 討論王傑唱法轉變及小提琴哭腔技巧","createTime":"2019-02-06T23:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T22:29:42.000Z","uid":52477,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"908a0070d9923991b209f7a671c2627911e5f65c","tid":1011534,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T23:36:48.000Z","msg":"樓豬係業餘人士，無學過樂理同唱歌。<br />\n亦因如此，只有拋磚引玉既能力，下面歡迎騎劫。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>LIVE回顧</strong></span><br />\n1988 王傑現場版 一場遊戲一場夢<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yWhseAjhJYo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyWhseAjhJYo&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=e1f8289d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yWhseAjhJYo</a><br />\n<br />\n1991 家太遠了 王傑(HQ)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O3_QmINPR7A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DO3_QmINPR7A&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=92d59d09\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O3_QmINPR7A</a><br />\n<br />\n1994 為了愛夢一生 王傑<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sMqr_CDGD_c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsMqr_CDGD_c&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=98f68723\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sMqr_CDGD_c</a><br />\n<br />\n2000 Hello@cash 歌曲 王傑(HQ)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s32HGSRcQi4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Ds32HGSRcQi4&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=c4ec4606\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s32HGSRcQi4</a><br />\n<br />\n2001 王傑 2001香港演唱会 谁明浪子心<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8sbHG7d0HYg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8sbHG7d0HYg&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=b2a0d10e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8sbHG7d0HYg</a><br />\n<br />\n2004 忘了你忘了我(中華情演唱)-王傑<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tSemUptS5wk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtSemUptS5wk&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=f3791090\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tSemUptS5wk</a><br />\n<br />\n2005 春節聯歡晚會 我比他好 王傑<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7L_eXxNUZo8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7L_eXxNUZo8&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=e456e67a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7L_eXxNUZo8</a><br />\n<br />\n2005/1999 王杰/容祖儿 还有 2005 vs 1999<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AY0ae2EuShk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAY0ae2EuShk&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=30bb1d57\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AY0ae2EuShk</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">專訪回顧</span></strong><br />\n王傑談唱歌方式<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gBy79OnbYVk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgBy79OnbYVk&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=99820e15\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gBy79OnbYVk</a><br />\n<br />\n2005 音樂前線 王傑專訪<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DrsVwgTZ07o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDrsVwgTZ07o&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=c86c98b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DrsVwgTZ07o</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>相關文章</strong></span><br />\n1。关于王杰前期和后期的唱法问题？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/21046020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhihu.com%2Fquestion%2F21046020&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=fd3856cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/21046020</a><br />\n王杰声音的转折点是《爱与梦》这张专辑，之前声音的变化都是渐进的，从早年高亢（个人定义为出道的前三年）到中期忧郁深情（飞碟后期、波丽佳音时期、英皇初期），直到进入英皇初期还可以唱《伤心1999》这样声音很高气息也要求很高的歌。<br />\n<br />\n2。[k歌技术交流]开个贴大家交流下技术,另对timrock音乐理论的几点怀疑大家讨论一下<br />\n<a href=\"https://bbs.hupu.com/511383.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbbs.hupu.com%2F511383.html&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=49747581\" target=\"_blank\">https://bbs.hupu.com/511383.html</a><br />\n王杰的《一场游戏一场梦》，在此我向各位介绍一个专业词汇，叫做&ldquo;关闭唱法&rdquo;。对于这种玄门正宗的高音唱法，王杰虽然掌握的不能算很专业，但也算有了七分火候，完全可以作为教学示范，毕竟大陆目前还找不到哪怕一个炉火纯青的关闭唱法高手，刘欢天赋太强，不适合作为学习对象，其余高手都在欧美，中文和英文唱法有所差异，初学者不建议模仿。<br />\n<br />\n3。王傑的演唱技巧 <br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/entertainment/blq53kn.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fentertainment%2Fblq53kn.html&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=7fcd2482\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/entertainment/blq53kn.html</a><br />\n王傑演唱歌曲的方式屬於那種比較直接的，基本上使用技巧不多，完全憑藉出色的嗓音完成。<br />\n<br />\n4。為什麼說王傑的唱功好？ <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.uknow01.com/p20180204065160361/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uknow01.com%2Fp20180204065160361%2F&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=92f7bcdd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.uknow01.com/p20180204065160361/</a><br />\n從專業的角度來講，王傑唱歌給人感覺好聽主要是三個原因：他的音色，他的唱法，他的樂感。"},{"pid":"fc483e97434e542f34529727f4f197e5c5fef08c","tid":1011534,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T23:40:15.000Z","msg":"有無王傑作曲技巧分析，連啲鬼佬都要抄佢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ib9d7stmvJE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIb9d7stmvJE&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=f64ad1db\" target=\"_blank\">https://